es" below.'=>'注意：此复选框启用所有阻止/限制功能，包括IP，国家和高级阻止，以及下面的“速率限制规则”。','HTML tags will be stripped prior to output and line breaks will be converted into the appropriate tags.'=>'HTML元素标签将在输出之前被剥离，换行符将被转换为适当的标记。','Prevent discovery of usernames through \'/?author=N\' scans, the oEmbed API, the WordPress REST API, and WordPress XML Sitemaps'=>'防止通过 \'/?author=N\' 扫描、指定oEmbed API、WordPress REST API 和 WordPress XML 站点地图发现用户名','Prevent users registering \'admin\' username if it doesn\'t exist'=>'屏蔽用户注册“admin”用户名(如果不存在)','Force all members to use strong passwords'=>'强制所有成员使用强密码','Force admins and publishers to use strong passwords (recommended)'=>'强制管理员和发布者使用强密码（推荐）','Additional Options'=>'其他选项','For all users with "publish posts" capability'=>'适用于具有“发布文章”功能的所有用户','For admins only'=>'仅限超级管理员','Hit enter to add a username'=>'按Enter键添加用户名','This option enables all "Brute Force Protection" options, including strong password enforcement and invalid login throttling. You can modify individual options below.'=>'此选项支持所有"暴力破解保护"选项，包括强密码强制和无效登录限制。您可以修改下面的单个选项。','Premium Feature:'=>'高级功能：','The plugin will load as a regular plugin after WordPress has been loaded, and while it can block many malicious requests, some vulnerable plugins or WordPress itself may run vulnerable code before all plugins are loaded.'=>'该插件将在加载WordPress后作为常规插件加载，虽然它可以阻止许多恶意请求，但是一些易受攻击的插件或WordPress本身可能会在加载所有插件之前运行易受攻击的代码。','Basic WordPress Protection:'=>'基本的WordPress保护：','Optimize the Wordfence Firewall'=>'优化Wordfence防火墙','You are currently running the Wordfence Web Application Firewall from another WordPress installation. Please configure the firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您当前正在从另一个WordPress安装运行Wordfence Web应用进程防火墙。 请将防火墙配置为在此站点上正确运行。','Existing WAF Installation Detected:'=>'检测到现有WAF安装：','Remove Extended Protection'=>'删除扩展保护','All PHP requests will be processed by the firewall prior to running.'=>'所有PHP请求都将在运行之前由防火墙处理。','Extended Protection:'=>'扩展保护：','Protection Level'=>'保护等级','Automatically enable on'=