nd errors, and are clearly engaged in malicious activity is an effective way to protect your site during an attack.'=>'Wordfence国家拦截被设计用来阻止攻击，防止内容盗窃，或者在不到30万分之一秒的时间内结束来自某个地理区域的恶意活动。封锁那些经常创建失败登录、大量页面未找到错误、且明显从事恶意活动的国家，是在攻击期间保护您的站点的有效方法。','Block Duration'=>'屏蔽时长','Country Blocking'=>'国家/地区拦截','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Custom </span>Pattern'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">自定义</span>模式','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Visitors Matching this Pattern</span>'=>'屏蔽<span class="wf-hidden-xs">匹配此模式的访客</span>','Country'=>'国家/地区','Update<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Block</span>'=>'更新<span class="wf-hidden-xs">拦截屏蔽规则</span>','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> the Selected Countries</span>'=>'屏蔽<span class="wf-hidden-xs">这些被选中的国家</span>','IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Address</span>'=>'IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs">地址</span>','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> this IP Address</span>'=>'屏蔽<span class="wf-hidden-xs">这个IP地址</span>','Are you sure you want to stop blocking the ${count} selected IPs, ranges, and countries?'=>'您确定要停止屏蔽${count}所选的IP，范围和国家/地区吗？','Are you sure you want to stop blocking the selected IP, range, or country?'=>'您确定要停止屏蔽所选的IP，范围或国家/地区吗？','Unblocking'=>'解除封锁中','Change Filter'=>'修改过滤','Clear Filter'=>'清空过滤条件','No blocks match the current filter.'=>'当前过滤器没有可匹配到屏蔽信息。','No blocks are currently active.'=>'目前没有任何被拦截的信息。','Last Attempt'=>'最后一次尝试','Block Count'=>'屏蔽计数','Expiration'=>'失效','Reason'=>'原因','Rule Added'=>'规则被添加的时间','Detail'=>'详情','Block Type'=>'屏蔽类型','Export<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> All IPs</span>'=>'导出<span class="wf-hidden-xs">所有IP </span>','Make Permanent'=>'手动永久屏蔽','Unblock'=>'取消屏蔽','Filter'=>'过滤','Filter by Type, Detail, or Reason'=>'按类型，详细信息或原因筛选','Show<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> Automatic<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Blocks</span>'=>'显示<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span>自动<span class="wf-hidden-xs">屏蔽</span>','Current blocks<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> for %s</span>'=>'当前被<span class="wf-hidden-xs">%s</span>屏蔽的黑名单','* User counts currently only reflect the main site on multisite installations.'=>'* 用户计数目前仅反映多站点安装的主站点。','Total Users'=>'用户总数','Role'=>'角色','Manage Users'=>'管理用户','User Summary'=>'用户摘要','If enabled, all settings and 2FA records will be deleted on deactivation. If later reactivated, all users that previously had 2FA active will need to set it up again.'=>'如果启用，所有设置和双重安全机制记录将在停用时删除。如果稍后重新激活，以前处于活动状态的所有用户都需要重新设置它。','Delete Login Security tables and data on deactivation'=>'停用后删除登录安全性的表和数据','While in test mode, reCAPTCHA will score login and registration requests but not actually block them. The scores will be recorded and can be used to select a human/bot threshold value.'=>'在测试模式下，reCAPTCHA将对登录和注册请求进行评分，但不会实际阻止它们。分数将被记录下来，并可用于选择一个人类/机器人的阈值。','Run reCAPTCHA in test mode'=>'在测试模式下运行reCAPTCHA','Disable XML-RPC authentication'=>'禁用XML-RPC身份验证','Required'=>'必填','Skipped'=>'跳过','If enabled, XML-RPC calls that require authentication will also require a valid 2FA code to be appended to the password. You must choose the "Skipped" option if you use the WordPress app, the Jetpack plugin, or other services that require XML-RPC.'=>'如果启用，需要身份验证的 XML-RPC 调用还需要将有效的双重安全机制代码追加到密码中。如果您使用 WordPress 应用、Jetpack 插件或其他需要 XML-RPC 的服务，则必须选择"跳过"选项。','Require 2FA for XML-RPC call authentication'=>'XML-RPC 调用身份验证需要双重安全机制','If enabled, users with 2FA enabled may choose to be prompted for a code only once every 30 days per device.'=>'如果启用，启用双重安全机制的用户可以选择每 30 天仅提示用户一次代码。','Allow remembering device for 30 days'=>'允许设备保留30天记忆','Super Administrator'=>'超级管理员','Save<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline"> Changes</span>'=>'保存<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline">更改</span>','Cancel<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline"> Changes</span>'=>'取消<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline">更改</span>','Detected IP:'=>'检测到的IP：','Corrected Time (WF):'=>'纠正时间(WF):','Corrected Time (NTP):'=>'纠正时间（NTP）：','Browser Time:'=>'浏览器时间：','Server Time:'=>'服务器时间：','(you)'=>'(您)','Editing User:&nbsp;&nbsp;%s <span class="wfls-text-plain">%s</span>'=>'编辑用户。 %s <span class="wfls-text-plain">%s</span>','Two-Factor Authentication, or 2FA, significantly improves login security for your website. Wordfence 2FA works with a number of TOTP-based apps like Google Authenticator, FreeOTP, and Authy. For a full list of tested TOTP-based apps, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here</a>.'=>'双因素认证，或2FA，显著提高了您网站的登录安全性。Wordfence 2FA可与许多基于TOTP的应用程序配合使用，如Google Authenticator、FreeOTP和Authy。有关基于TOTP的测试应用程序的完整列表，请<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">点击这里</a>。','Premium Feature'=>'高级功能','An error was encountered while trying to send the notification. Please try again.'=>'在尝试发送通知时遇到了错误。请再试一次。','Notification Sent'=>'已发送通知','Error Sending Notification'=>'错误发送通知','These IPs (or CIDR ranges) will be ignored when determining the requesting IP via the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header. Enter one IP or CIDR range per line.'=>'通过X-Forwarded-For HTTP标头确定请求IP时，将忽略这些IP（或CIDR范围）。 每行输入一个IP或CIDR范围。','How to get IPs'=>'如何获得IP','Use the X-Real-IP HTTP header. Only use if you have a front-end proxy or spoofing may result.'=>'使用X-Real-IP HTTP标头。 仅在您拥有前端代理时才使用，否则可能会导致欺骗。','Use the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header. Only use if you have a front-end proxy or spoofing may result.'=>'使用X-Forwarded-For HTTP标头。 仅在您拥有前端代理时才使用，否则可能会导致欺骗。','Use PHP\'s built in REMOTE_ADDR and don\'t use anything else. Very secure if this is compatible with your site.'=>'使用PHP内置的REMOTE_ADDR，不要使用其他任何东西。 如果这与您的网站兼容，则非常安全。','(Recommended)'=>'（推荐）','Use the most secure method to get visitor IP addresses. Prevents spoofing and works with most sites.'=>'使用最安全的方法获取访问者IP地址。防止欺骗，适用于大多数网站。','reCAPTCHA v3 Secret'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 Secret','reCAPTCHA v3 Site Key'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 站点密钥','reCAPTCHA v3 does not make users solve puzzles or click a checkbox like previous versions. The only visible part is the reCAPTCHA logo. If a visitor\'s browser fails the CAPTCHA, Wordfence will send an email to the user\'s address with a link they can click to verify that they are a user of your site. You can read further details <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">in our documentation</a>.'=>'reCAPTCHA v3并不像以前的版本那样让用户解开谜题或点击复选框。唯一可见的部分是reCAPTCHA标志。如果访问者的浏览器未能通过验证码，Wordfence将向用户的地址发送一封电子邮件，其中包含一个链接，用户可以点击该链接来验证他们是否是您网站的用户。您可以<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">在我们的文档中</a>阅读更多细节。','Enable reCAPTCHA on the login and user registration pages'=>'在登录和用户注册页面上启用reCAPTCHA','Count'=>'数量','reCAPTCHA Score History'=>'reCAPTCHA的得分历史','Requests'=>'请求','Reset Score Statistics'=>'重置分数统计','A reCAPTCHA score equal to or higher than this value will be considered human. Anything lower will be treated as a bot and require additional verification for login and registration.'=>'等于或高于该值的reCAPTCHA分数将被视为人类。 较低的任何内容都将被视为漫游器，并且需要其他验证才能登录和注册。','reCAPTCHA human/bot threshold score'=>'reCAPTCHA人/机器人阈值分数','0.2'=>'0.2','0.3'=>'0.3','0.4'=>'0.4','0.5 (probably a human)'=>'0.5 （可能是人类）','0.6'=>'0.6','0.7'=>'0.7','0.8'=>'0.8','0.9'=>'0.9','1.0 (definitely a human)'=>'1.0 （绝对是人类）','You have just installed the Wordfence Login Security plugin. It contains a subset of the functionality found in the full Wordfence plugin: Two-factor Authentication, XML-RPC Protection and Login Page CAPTCHA.'=>'您刚刚安装了Wordfence登录安全插件。它包含了完整的Wordfence插件中的部分功能。双因素验证、XML-RPC保护和登录页面验证码。','Wordfence Login Security Installed'=>'安装了Wordfence登录安全','An error was encountered while trying to generate new recovery codes. Please try again.'=>'在尝试生成新的恢复代码时遇到了错误。请再试一次。','New Recovery Codes'=>'新的恢复代码','Error Generating New Codes'=>'新代码生成错误','Generate'=>'生成','Are you sure you want to generate new recovery codes? Any remaining unused codes will be disabled.'=>'您确定要生成新的恢复代码吗？任何剩余的未使用的代码将被禁用。','If you\'re looking for a more comprehensive solution, the <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">full Wordfence plugin</a> includes all of the features in this plugin as well as a full-featured WordPress firewall, a security scanner, live traffic, and more. The standard installation includes a robust set of free features that can be upgraded via a Premium license key.'=>'如果您正在寻找一个更全面的解决方案，<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">完整的Wordfence插件</a>包括这个插件中的所有功能，以及一个全功能的WordPress防火墙，一个安全扫描仪，实时流量等。标准安装包括一套强大的免费功能，可以通过高级许可密钥进行升级。','Generate New Recovery Codes'=>'生成新的恢复代码','Generate New Codes'=>'生成新代码','Recovery Codes'=>'恢复代码','An error was encountered while trying to deactivate two-factor authentication. Please try again.'=>'在尝试停用双因素认证时遇到错误。请再试一次。','Error Deactivating 2FA'=>'停用2FA时出错','Are you sure you want to deactivate two-factor authentication?'=>'您确定要停用双因素认证吗？','Deactivate 2FA'=>'停用2FA','Deactivate'=>'禁用','Wordfence two-factor authentication is currently active on the account <strong>%s</strong>. You may deactivate it by clicking the button below.'=>'帐户上的Wordfence双因素认证目前处于激活状态。 <strong>%s</strong>.您可以通过点击下面的按钮将其停用。','Wordfence two-factor authentication is currently active on your account. You may deactivate it by clicking the button below.'=>'Wordfence双因素认证目前在您的账户上处于激活状态。您可以通过点击下面的按钮来停用它。','Wordfence 2FA Active'=>'激活的Wordfence 2FA','1. Scan Code or Enter Key'=>'1、扫描码或输入Key','Skip'=>'跳过','Reminder: If you lose access to your authenticator device, you can use recovery codes to log in. If you have not saved a copy of your recovery codes, we recommend downloading them now.'=>'提醒如果您失去了对认证器设备的访问权限，您可以使用恢复码进行登录。如果您还没有保存恢复码的副本，我们建议您现在下载。','An error was encountered while trying to activate two-factor authentication. Please try again.'=>'在尝试激活双因素认证时遇到错误。请再试一次。','Error Activating 2FA'=>'激活双重安全机制出错','For help on setting up an app, visit our help article.'=>'有关设置应用程序的帮助，请访问我们的帮助文章。','Enter the code from your authenticator app below to verify and activate two-factor authentication for this account.'=>'在下面的验证器应用中输入代码，验证并激活该账户的双因素验证。','Two-Factor Authentication Recovery Codes - %s (%s)'=>'双因素认证恢复码-%s (%s)','Use one of these %d codes to log in if you lose access to your authenticator device. Codes are %d characters long plus optional spaces. Each one may be used only once.'=>'如果您失去了对身份验证器设备的访问权限，请使用这些%d代码之一进行登录。代码长度为%d个字符，外加可选的空格。每个代码只能使用一次。','Each line of %d letters and numbers is a single recovery code, with optional spaces for readability. To use a recovery code, after entering your username and password, enter the code like "1234 5678 90AB CDEF" at the 2FA prompt. If your site has a custom login prompt and does not show a 2FA prompt, you can use the single-step method by entering your password and the code together in the Password field, like "mypassword1234 5678 90AB CDEF". Your recovery codes are:'=>'每一行%d字母和数字都是一个恢复码，为了便于阅读，可以选择空格。使用恢复码时，在输入用户名和密码后，在2FA提示下输入 "1234 5678 90AB CDEF "等代码。如果您的网站有自定义登录提示，没有显示2FA提示，您可以使用单步法，在密码栏里把密码和代码一起输入，比如 "mypassword1234 5678 90AB CDEF"。您的恢复码是','Optional'=>'选项','Download Recovery Codes'=>'下载恢复代码','2. Enter Code from Authenticator App'=>'2、从认证器应用程序中输入代码','The request was flagged as suspicious, and we need verification that you attempted to log in to allow it to proceed. This verification link <b>will be valid for 15 minutes</b> from the time it was sent. If you did not attempt this login, please change your password immediately.'=>'该请求被标记为可疑，我们需要验证您是否尝试登录以允许其继续。此验证链接的<b>有效期为发送后15分钟</b>。如果您没有尝试此次登录，请立即更改密码。','IP:'=>'IP：','Request Time:'=>'请求时间：','<a class="wfls-btn wfls-btn-default wfls-btn-sm wfls-dismiss-link" href="#" onclick="GWFLS.dismiss_notice(\'%s\'); return false;">Dismiss</a>'=>'<a class="wfls-btn wfls-btn-default wfls-btn-sm wfls-dismiss-link" href="#" onclick="GWFLS.dismiss_notice(\'%s\'); return false;">放弃</a>','Learn more<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> about Login Security</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> 关于登录安全的信息</span>','Login Security Settings'=>'登录安全设置','Settings'=>'设置','Learn more<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> about Two-Factor Authentication</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> 关于双因素认证的信息</span>','Login Security'=>'登录安全性：为这些角色启用双重安全机制','Email verification invalid or expired. Please try again.'=>'电子邮件验证无效或过期。请重试。','Email verification succeeded. Please continue logging in.'=>'电子邮件验证成功。请继续登录。','<strong>REGISTRATION BLOCKED</strong>: The registration request was blocked because it was flagged as spam. Please try again or contact the site owner for help.'=>'<strong>注册被阻止</strong>：注册请求被阻止，因为它被标记为垃圾邮件。请再试一次或联系网站所有者寻求帮助。','<strong>REGISTRATION BLOCKED</strong>: The registration request was blocked because it was flagged as spam. Please try again or <a href="#" class="wfls-registration-captcha-contact" data-token="%s">contact the site owner</a> for help.'=>'<strong>注册被阻止</strong>：注册请求被阻止，因为它被标记为垃圾邮件。请再试一次或<a href="#" class="wfls-registration-captcha-contact" data-token="%s">联系网站所有者</a>寻求帮助。','<strong>REGISTRATION ATTEMPT BLOCKED</strong>: The security token for the login attempt was invalid or expired. Please reload the page and try again.'=>'<strong>注册尝试被阻止</strong>：登录尝试的安全令牌无效或过期。请重新加载页面并再次尝试。','<strong>REGISTRATION ATTEMPT BLOCKED</strong>: This site requires a security token created when the page loads for all registration attempts. Please ensure JavaScript is enabled and try again.'=>'<strong>注册尝试被阻止</strong>：本网站需要在页面加载时为所有注册尝试创建一个安全令牌。请确保JavaScript已启用，并再次尝试。','You do not currently have two-factor authentication active on your account, which will be required beginning %s. <a href="%s">Configure 2FA</a>'=>'您的账户上目前没有激活双因素身份验证，从%s 开始，您需要激活双因素身份验证。<a href="%s">配置2FA</a>','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please provide your 2FA code when prompted.'=>'<strong>代码要求</strong>。请在提示时提供您的2FA代码。','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please enter your 2FA code immediately after your password in the same field.'=>'<strong>代码要求</strong>。请在密码后的同一栏目中输入您的2FA代码。','<strong>CODE INVALID</strong>: The 2FA code provided is either expired or invalid. Please try again.'=>'<strong>代码无效</strong>：所提供的2FA代码过期或无效。请重试。','Login Verification Required'=>'登录验证要求','Manage 2FA Settings'=>'管理2FA设置','Two-factor authentication is not currently enabled for this account type. To enable it, visit the Wordfence 2FA Settings page.'=>'目前尚未为该账户类型启用双因素验证。要