est was received to stop the previous scan from Wordfence Central.'=>'SUM_KILL:收到来自Wordfare Central的停止上一次扫描的请求。','Scan stop request received from Wordfence Central.'=>'扫描从 Wordfence Central收到的停止请求。','Wordfence scan starting at %s from Wordfence Central'=>'从Wordfence Central从%s 开始的Wordfence扫描','Number of scan results to return.'=>'要返回的扫描结果数量。','Offset of scan results to return.'=>'要返回的扫描结果的偏移量。','Scan result group or all results.'=>'扫描结果组或所有结果。','Validation error: \'fields\' parameter is empty or not an array.'=>'验证错误：\'field\'参数为空或不是数组。','A server error occurred while saving the configuration: %s'=>'保存配置时发生服务器错误：%s','Errors occurred while saving the configuration.'=>'保存配置时发生错误。','Errors occurred while saving the configuration: %s'=>'保存配置时发生错误：%s','An error occurred while saving the configuration: %s'=>'保存配置时发生错误：%s','Specific config options to set.'=>'要设置的特定配置选项。','Specific config options to return.'=>'要返回的特定配置选项。','Authorization header format is invalid.'=>'授权标头格式无效。','Token is invalid.'=>'令牌无效。','Admin user with this email address not found.'=>'找不到这个电子邮件地址的管理用户。','Email address is invalid.'=>'无效的电邮地址。','Signature is invalid.'=>'签名无效。','Nonce is invalid.'=>'随机数无效。','Site ID is invalid.'=>'网站ID无效。','Nonce format is invalid.'=>'随机格式无效。','Data is invalid.'=>'数据无效。','Site is not connected to Wordfence Central.'=>'站点未连接到 Wordfence Central。','Connect Site'=>'连接网站','To connect your site your site to Wordfence Central, use the link below:'=>'要将您的网站连接到 Wordfence Central，请使用以下链接：','Disconnect Site'=>'断开网站','Wordfence Central Installation Process'=>'Wordfence Central安装过程','Wordfence Central'=>'Wordfence Central','Redirecting back to Wordfence Central.'=>'重定向回Wordfence Central。','Retrieving access token using authorization grant.'=>'使用授权许可检索访问令牌。','Testing that Wordfence Central is able to communicate with this site.'=>'测试Wordfence Central是否能与本网站进行通信。','Testing public key authentication with Wordfence Central.'=>'用Wordfence Central测试公钥认证。','Passing public key to Wordfence Central.'=>'将公钥传给Wordfence Central。','Testing initial communication with Wordfence Central.'=>'测试与Wordfence Central的初步沟通。','You\'ve chosen to block the network that <span style="color: #F00;">%s</span> is part of. We\'ve marked the networks we found that this IP address belongs to in red below. Make sure you read all the WHOIS information so that you see all networks this IP belongs to. We recommend blocking the network with the lowest number of addresses. You may find this is listed at the end as part of the \'rWHOIS\' query which contacts the local WHOIS server that is run by the network administrator.'=>'您已选择阻止<span style="color: #F00;">%s</span> 所属的网络。 我们已经标记了我们发现此IP地址属于以下红色的网络。 确保您阅读了所有WHOIS信息，以便查看此IP所属的所有网络。 我们建议使用最少的地址阻止网络。 您可能会发现最终将此列为“rWHOIS”查询的一部分，该查询与网络管理员运行的本地WHOIS服务器联系。','How to block a network'=>'如何屏蔽一个网络','The whois service gives you a way to look up who owns an IP address or domain name that is visiting your website or is engaging in malicious activity on your website.'=>'Whois服务为您提供了一种查找谁拥有访问您的网站或在您的网站上从事恶意活动的ip地址或域名的方法。','Your site is now using the legacy two-factor authentication system.'=>'您的网站现在使用的是传统的双因素认证系统。','Legacy Two-Factor Authentication Active'=>'旧版双重身份认证模式启用','Revert'=>'恢复','All two-factor authentication settings and users\' codes will revert to your older settings. If any users had set up two-factor authentication after the update, they will no longer have 2FA enabled until you switch to the new version again.'=>'所有双因素认证设置和用户代码将恢复到您的旧设置。如果有用户在更新后设置了双因素身份验证，他们将不再启用2FA，直到您再次切换到新版本。','Revert back to legacy two-factor authentication?'=>'是否恢复到传统的双因素身份验证？','Automatic migration of the 2FA-enabled accounts failed. Please verify that your server is reachable via the internet and try again.'=>'启用双重身份认证模式的帐户的自动迁移失败。请验证您的服务器是否可通过互联网连接，然后重试。','Migration Failed'=>'迁移失败','One or more users with two-factor authentication active are using SMS, which is unsupported in the new login security module. Please either deactivate two-factor authentication for those users or change them to use an authenticator app prior to migration.'=>'一个或多个激活了双因素认证的用户正在使用短信，而新的登录安全模块不支持短信。请为这些用户停用双因素认证，或在迁移前将其改为使用认证器应用。','Migration Cannot Proceed'=>'无法进行迁移','Go To New 2FA'=>'转到新双重身份认证模式','Your site is now using the new login security module and two-factor authentication. Before logging out, we recommend testing your login in a different browser or a private/incognito window. If any plugins or your theme cause conflicts with logging in, you can revert to the old 2FA method.'=>'您的网站现在使用新的登录安全模块和双因素认证。在注销之前，我们建议在不同的浏览器或私人/隐身窗口测试您的登录。如果任何插件或您的主题导致登录冲突，您可以恢复到旧的2FA方法。','New Two-Factor Authentication Active'=>'新双重身份认证模式启用','Switch'=>'开关','Migrate'=>'迁移','Migrate or switch to new two-factor authentication?'=>'迁移或切换到新的双因素身份验证？','Use the buttons below to migrate to the new two-factor authentication system or switch without migration. Migration will copy all existing authenticator-based user activations over to the new system while switching will use only users already set up in the new system. Existing SMS-based two-factor authentication activations must be disabled prior to migration.'=>'使用下面的按钮迁移到新的双因素认证系统，或者不迁移而切换。迁移将把所有现有的基于身份验证器的用户激活复制到新系统中，而切换将只使用已经在新系统中设置的用户。在迁移之前，必须禁用现有的基于短信的双因素身份验证激活。','Revert to Legacy 2FA'=>'还原到旧版双重身份认证模式','If you have a conflict with the new 2FA method, you can temporarily switch back to the Legacy version.'=>'如果与新的双重身份认证模式有冲突，可以暂时切换回旧版。','Legacy support for SMS-based two-factor authentication is being phased out, as it is less secure than using a modern authenticator app.'=>'对基于短信的双因素身份验证的传统支持正在逐步取消，因为它比使用现代身份验证应用进程更不安全。','2FA Mode: Normal'=>'双重身份认证模式：常规','No users currently have cellphone sign-in enabled.'=>'目前没有用户启用手机登录。','Activate'=>'启用','Code'=>'代码','Enter activation code:'=>'输入激活码：','Cellphone Sign-in Enabled'=>'手机登录已启用','Authenticator'=>'认证','Phone (%s)'=>'电话（ %s）','Two-Factor Authentication Users'=>'双重素身份验证用户','+1 (000) 000 0000'=>'+1 (000) 000 0000','Send code to a phone number:'=>'将代码发送到电话号码：','Use authenticator app'=>'使用身份验证器应用','Enter username to enable Two-Factor Authentication for'=>'输入用户名以启用双因素认证，用于','Enable Two-Factor Authentication'=>'启用双重素身份验证','<strong>Note:</strong> Two-Factor Authentication is disabled when the option "Enable Brute Force Protection" is off.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>当选项"启用暴力破解保护"关闭时，将禁用双重身份验证。','Are you sure you want to restore the default Two-Factor Authentication settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page. If you have configured any users to use two-factor authentication, they will not be changed.'=>'您确定要恢复默认的双因素认证设置吗？这将撤销您对本页选项所做的任何自定义更改。如果您已将任何用户配置为使用双因素身份验证，它们将不会被更改。','With Two-Factor Authentication enabled, an attacker needs to know your username, password <em>and</em> have control of your phone to log in to your site. We recommend you enable Two-Factor Authentication for all Administrator level accounts.'=>'启用双因素认证后，攻击者需要知道您的用户名、密码<em>并</em>控制您的手机才能登录您的网站。我们建议您为所有管理员级别的账户启用双因素认证。','Take Login Security to the next level with Two-Factor Authentication'=>'通过双因素身份验证将登录安全性提升到一个新水平','Switch to New 2FA'=>'切换到新双重身份认证模式','Two-factor authentication is using legacy support, which enables SMS-based codes but is less compatible. An improved interface and use by non-administrators is available by activating the new login security module.'=>'双因素认证使用的是传统的支持，可以使用基于短信的代码，但兼容性较差。通过激活新的登录安全模块，可以改进接口和非管理员使用。','Used by banks, government agencies, and military worldwide, two-factor authentication is one of the most secure forms of remote system authentication available. With it enabled, an attacker needs to know your username, password, <em>and</em> have control of your phone to log into your site. Upgrade to Premium now to enable this powerful feature.'=>'全球银行，政府机构和军队使用的双重身份验证是可用的最安全的远程系统身份验证形式之一。 启用该功能后，攻击者需要知道您的用户名，密码，<em>和</em>对您的手机具有控制权才能登录到您的站点。 立即升级到高级版以启用此强大功能。','2FA Mode: Legacy'=>'双重身份认证模式：旧版','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Two-Factor Authentication</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wf-hidden-xs">关于双因素认证的信息</span>','Live traffic now defaults to a summary view. Details are viewable by clicking anywhere within the summary record. To switch to the expanded view, click the <strong>Expand All Records</strong> switch. New installations will only log security-related traffic by default, though your previous setting has been preserved.'=>'实时流量现在默认为摘要视图。 通过单击摘要记录中的任何位置可查看详细信息。 要切换到展开式视图，请单击<strong>展开所有记录</strong>开关。 默认情况下，新安装仅会记录与安全相关的流量，但您之前的设置已被保留。','Live traffic defaults to a summary view of all security-related traffic. Details are viewable by clicking anywhere within the summary record. To switch to the expanded view, click the <strong>Expand All Records</strong> switch.'=>'实时流量默认为所有与安全相关的流量的摘要视图。 通过单击摘要记录中的任何位置可查看详细信息。 要切换到展开式视图，请单击<strong>展开所有记录</strong>开关。','Recent'=>'最新','See recent traffic'=>'查看最近的流量','Expand All Results'=>'展开所有结果','Show Advanced Filters'=>'显示高级过滤器','Blocked'=>'阻止','Warning'=>'警告','Bot'=>'机器人','Human'=>'人类','Regular traffic and security-related traffic will appear below.'=>'常规流量和与安全相关的流量将显示在下方。','Traffic logging mode: All traffic'=>'流量记录模式：所有流量','Login and firewall activity will appear below.'=>'登录和防火墙活动将显示在下方。','Traffic logging mode: Security-related traffic only'=>'流量记录模式：仅与安全相关的流量','Click inside window to resume'=>'单击窗口内部以恢复','Live Updates Paused'=>'暂停实时更新','To clone one site\'s configuration to another, use the import/export tools below.'=>'要将一个站点的配置克隆到另一个站点，请使用下面的导入/导出工具。','Restore<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Defaults</span>'=>'恢复<span class="wf-hidden-xs">默认值</span>','Are you sure you want to restore the default Diagnostics settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page.'=>'您确定要恢复默认的诊断设置吗？ 这将撤消您对此页面上的选项所做的任何自定义更改。','Wordfence Live Traffic shows you what is happening on your site in real-time, including user logins, hack attempts, and requests that were blocked by the Wordfence Firewall. You can choose to log security-related traffic only or all traffic. Traffic is logged directly on the server, which means it includes visits that don\'t execute JavaScript. Google and other JavaScript-based analytics packages typically only show visits from browsers that are operated by a human, while Live Traffic can show visits from crawlers like Google and Bing.'=>'Wordfence实时流量会实时显示您网站上发生的情况，包括用户登录，黑客尝试以及Wordfence防火墙阻止的请求。 您可以选择仅记录与安全相关的流量或所有流量。 流量直接记录在服务器上，这意味着它包括不执行JavaScript的访问。 Google和其他基于JavaScript的分析软件包通常仅显示由人工操作的浏览器的访问，而实时流量可以显示来自Google和Bing等爬虫的访问。','Confirm Restore Defaults'=>'确认恢复默认值','Save Changes'=>'保存修改','Cancel Changes'=>'取消更改','Restore Defaults'=>'恢复默认值','Disable reading of php://input'=>'禁用读取php://input','Enable SSL Verification (Disable this if you are consistently unable to connect to the Wordfence servers.)'=>'启用SSL验证（如果始终无法连接到Wordfence服务器，请禁用此功能。）','Start all scans remotely (Try this if your scans aren\'t starting and your site is publicly accessible)'=>'远程启动所有扫描（如果您的扫描未启动且您的站点可公开访问，请尝试此操作）','Enable debugging mode (increases database load)'=>'启用调试模式（增加数据库负载）','Debugging Options'=>'调试选项','Clear all Wordfence Central connection data'=>'清除所有的Wordfence Central连接数据','Send Test Activity Report'=>'发送测试活动报告','Send a test activity report email:'=>'发送测试活动报告电子邮件：','Send Test Email'=>'发送测试邮件','Send a test email from this WordPress server to an email address:'=>'将测试电子邮件从此WordPress服务器发送到电子邮件地址：','Test your WordPress host\'s available memory'=>'测试您的WordPress主机的可用内存','Click to view your system\'s configuration in a new window'=>'单击以在新窗口中查看系统的配置','System configuration, memory test, send test email from this server.'=>'系统配置，内存测试，从此服务器发送测试电子邮件。','Other Tests'=>'其他测试','No New Issues'=>'没有新问题','New Issues (%d total)'=>'新问题（总计%d）','Scan Issues'=>'扫描问题','Requires downloading from the server directly'=>'需要直接从服务器下载','UTC'=>'UTC','No log files found.'=>'没有发现日志文件。','Download'=>'下载','File'=>'文件','PHP error logs generated by your site, if enabled by your host.'=>'您的站点生成的PHP错误日志（如果您的主机已启用）。','Log Files'=>'日志文件','and %d more'=>'更多%d','regular case'=>'常规案例','lowercase'=>'小写','All Tables Exist