tinue using Defiant products and services including the Wordfence plugin, all customers must review and agree to the updated terms and privacy policies. These changes reflect our commitment to follow data protection best practices and regulations. The Wordfence interface will remain disabled until these terms are agreed to.'=>'要继续使用Defiant产品和服务（包括Wordfence插件），所有客户都必须查看并同意更新的条款和隐私政策。 这些变化反映了我们遵守数据保护最佳实践和法规的承诺。 在同意这些条款之前，Wordfence接口将保持禁用状态。','Agreement to New Terms and Privacy Policies'=>'同意新条款和隐私政策','General Data Protection Regulation'=>'通用数据保护条例','GDPR Information'=>'GDPR信息','Upgrade Now to Access Premium Support'=>'立即升级以访问高级支持','Our senior support engineers <strong>respond to Premium tickets within a few hours</strong> on average and have a direct line to our QA and development teams.'=>'我们的高级支持工程师<strong>平均在几小时内回复高级门票</strong>，并直接与我们的质量保证和开发团队联系。','Premium Support'=>'支持论坛','Go to Support Forums'=>'转到支持论坛','Support for free customers is available via our forums page on wordpress.org. The majority of requests <strong>receive an answer within a few days.</strong>'=>'可通过wordpress.org上的论坛页面获得对免费客户的支持。 大多数请求<strong>会在几天内收到答案。</strong>','Free Support'=>'免费支持','Track each scan stage as Wordfence scans your entire site. Along the way you can see the activity log one line at a time or expand the activity log for a more detailed view. Clicking on scan results will reveal detailed scan findings.'=>'当Wordfence扫描整个站点时，跟踪每个扫描阶段。 在此过程中，您可以一次查看活动日志一行，或者展开活动日志以获取更详细的视图。 单击扫描结果将显示详细的扫描结果。','Scan Progress and Activity'=>'扫描进度和活动','All of your scan options, including scheduling, are now located here.'=>'您的所有扫描选项（包括计划）现在都位于此处。','Scan Options &amp; Settings'=>'扫描选项＆amp;设置','By default, Wordfence will scan your site daily. Start your first scan now to see if your site has any security issues that need to be addressed. From here you can run manual scans any time you like.'=>'默认情况下，Wordfence将每天扫描您的网站。 立即开始第一次扫描，看看您的网站是否存在需要解决的任何安全问题。 从这里，您可以随时运行手动扫描。','Start Your First Scan'=>'开始您的第一次扫描','Set up the way you want the scan to monitor your site security including custom scan configurations and scheduling.'=>'设置扫描监控站点安全性的方式，包括自定义扫描配置和计划。','Manage Scan Settings'=>'管理扫描设置','A Wordfence scan looks for malware, malicious URLs, and patterns of infections by examining all of the files, posts, and comments on your WordPress website. It also checks your server and monitors your site\'s online reputation.'=>'Wordfence扫描通过检查WordPress网站上的所有文件，文章和评论来查找恶意软件，恶意URL和感染模式。 它还会检查您的服务器并监控您网站的在线声誉。','Repair Files'=>'修复文件','Do not repair files on your system unless you\'re ABSOLUTELY sure you know what you\'re doing. If you repair the wrong file it could cause your WordPress website to stop functioning and you will probably have to restore from backups. If you\'re unsure, Cancel and work with your hosting provider to clean your system of infected files.'=>'不要修复系统上的文件，除非您绝对确定您知道自己在做什么。 如果您修复了错误的文件，可能会导致WordPress网站停止运行，您可能需要从备份中恢复。 如果您不确定，请取消并与您的托管服务提供商合作，以清理您的受感染文件系统。','Close'=>'关闭','Are you sure you want to repair?'=>'您确定要修复？','Delete Files'=>'删除文件','<strong>WARNING:</strong> If you delete the wrong file, it could cause your WordPress website to stop functioning, and you will probably have to restore from a backup.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>如果删除了错误的文件，可能会导致WordPress网站停止运行，您可能需要从备份中恢复。','Are you sure you want to delete?'=>'您确定您要删除？','Manage scan options including scheduling'=>'管理扫描选项，包括计划','Scan Options and Scheduling'=>'扫描选项和计划','Reputation Check Status'=>'信誉检查状态','Manage Options'=>'管理选项','Reputation Checks'=>'信誉检查','Enable Premium Scan Signatures.'=>'启用高级扫描签名。','Malware Signatures Status'=>'恶意软件签名状态','Protect More Sites'=>'保护更多网站','Signature updates delayed by 30 days'=>'签名更新延迟30天','Signatures updated in real-time'=>'签名实时更新','Malware Signatures: '=>'恶意软件签名: ','https://www.wordfence.com/help/scan/#scan-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/scan/#scan-status','Scan Type: '=>'扫描类型: ','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about the Scanner</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wf-hidden-xs">关于扫描功能</span>','Importing and exporting of options is available on the Tools page'=>'“工具”页面上提供了选项的导入和导出','Tool Options'=>'工具选项','Scan Options'=>'扫描选项','These options are also available throughout the plugin pages, in the relevant sections. This page is provided for easier setup for experienced Wordfence users.'=>'这些选项也可在整个插件页面的相关章节中使用。 提供此页面是为了让有经验的Wordfence用户更容易设置。','Enable Separate Prompt for Two Factor Code'=>'启用双因素代码的单独提示','Require Cellphone Sign-in for all Administrators'=>'需要手机登录的所有管理员','Import Wordfence options from another site using a token'=>'使用令牌从其他站点导入Wordfence选项配置','Export this site\'s Wordfence options for import on another site'=>'导出此站点的Wordfence选项配置来导入另一个站点上','Maximum days to keep Live Traffic data'=>'保持实时流量数据的最长天数','Amount of Live Traffic data to store (number of rows)'=>'要存储的实时流量数据量（行数）','Browser user-agent to ignore'=>'忽略的浏览器用户代理(user-agent)','List of comma separated IP addresses to ignore'=>'要忽略的IP地址列表，英文逗号分隔IP地址','List of comma separated usernames to ignore'=>'要忽略的用户名列表，逗号分隔用户名','Don\'t log signed-in users with publishing access'=>'不要显示具有发布权限的用户','Traffic logging mode (Live Traffic)'=>'流量记录模式（实时流量）','Additional scan signatures'=>'其他扫描签名','Exclude files from scan that match these wildcard patterns'=>'从扫描中排除与这些通配符模式匹配的文件','Maximum execution time for each scan stage'=>'每个扫描阶段的最长执行时间','How much memory should Wordfence request when scanning'=>'扫描时Wordfence应该请求多少内存','Time limit that a scan can run in seconds'=>'运行扫描时间限制在多长的时间内','Limit the number of issues sent in the scan results email'=>'限制发送的电子邮件中扫描结果问题数量','Use low resource scanning (reduces server load by lengthening the scan duration)'=>'使用低资源扫描（通过延长扫描持续时间来减少服务器负载）','Scan images, binary, and other files as if they were executable'=>'扫描图像，二进制文件和其他文件，就像它们是可执行文件一样','Scan files outside your WordPress installation'=>'扫描WordPress安装之外的文件','Monitor Web Application Firewall status'=>'监视 Web 应用程序防火墙状态','Monitor disk space'=>'监控磁盘空间','Check the strength of passwords'=>'检查密码的强度','Scan for suspicious admin users created outside of WordPress'=>'扫描在 WordPress 之外创建的可疑管理员用户','Scan for out of date, abandoned, and vulnerable plugins, themes, and WordPress versions'=>'扫描过时，废弃和易受攻击的插件，主题和WordPress版本','Scan WordPress core, plugin, and theme options for known dangerous URLs and suspicious content'=>'扫描已知危险网址和可疑内容的WordPress内核，插件和主题选项','Scan comments for known dangerous URLs and suspicious content'=>'扫描已知危险网址和可疑内容的评论','Scan posts for known dangerous URLs and suspicious content'=>'扫描已知危险网址和可疑内容的文章','Scan file contents for malicious URLs'=>'扫描恶意网址的文件内容','Scan file contents for backdoors, trojans and suspicious code'=>'扫描后门，特洛伊木马和可疑代码的文件内容','Scan for signatures of known malicious files'=>'扫描已知恶意文件的签名','Scan wp-admin and wp-includes for files not bundled with WordPress'=>'扫描wp-admin和wp-includes目录，查找未与WordPress捆绑在一起的文件','Scan plugin files against repository versions for changes'=>'扫描针对存储库版本进行更改插件文件','Scan theme files against repository versions for changes'=>'扫描针对更改的存储库版本主题文件','Scan core files against repository versions for changes'=>'扫描针对存储库版本进行更改内核文件','Scan for publicly accessible quarantined files'=>'扫描可公开访问的隔离文件','Scan for publicly accessible configuration, backup, or log files'=>'扫描可公开访问的配置，备份或日志文件','Scan for misconfigured How does Wordfence get IPs'=>'扫描\'Wordfence如何获取客户端IP\'配置是否错误','Check if this website IP is generating spam'=>'检查此网站IP是否产生垃圾邮件','Check if this website is being &quot;Spamvertised&quot;'=>'检查本网站是否被&quot;滥发讯息&quot;','Scan Type'=>'扫描类型','Schedule Wordfence Scans'=>'安排Wordfence扫描','If user who is allowed to access the site views the relative URL ____ then set a cookie that will bypass country blocking in future in case that user hits the site from a blocked country'=>'如果允许访问该网站的用户查看相对 URL ____，则设置一个 Cookie，该 Cookie 将在将来绕过国家/地区阻止，以防该用户从被阻止的国家/地区访问网站','If user from a blocked country hits the relative URL ____ then redirect that user to ____ and set a cookie that will bypass all country blocking'=>'如果来自被屏蔽国家的用户点击了相对的网址____，那么将该用户重定向到____，并设置一个cookie来绕过所有国家的屏蔽','Block