','Pause live updates when window loses focus'=>'当鼠标移出插件浏览器窗口时暂停实时更新页面','Disable Code Execution for Uploads directory'=>'禁用上传（wp-content/uploads）目录的代码执行','Hide WordPress version'=>'隐藏WordPress版本','Trusted Proxies'=>'信任的代理','How does Wordfence get IPs'=>'Wordfence如何获得客户端IP(用户真实IP)','Where to email alerts'=>'通知邮件发送到哪里','Update Wordfence automatically when a new version is released?'=>'当Wordfence发布新版本时自动更新？','Display Live Traffic menu item'=>'显示实时浏览流量菜单项','Display Blocking menu item'=>'显示黑名单菜单项','Display All Options menu item'=>'显示所有选项菜单项','License Key'=>'许可证','All Options'=>'所有选项','Set up the way you want the firewall to protect your site including the web application firewall, brute force protection, rate limiting, and blocking.'=>'设置您希望防火墙保护您的站点的方式，包括Web应用进程防火墙，强力保护，速率限制和屏蔽。','Firewall Options'=>'防火墙选项','Wordfence protects your site from password-guessing attacks by locking out attackers and helping you avoid weak passwords.'=>'Wordfence通过锁定攻击者并帮助您避免弱密码来保护您的站点免受密码猜测攻击。','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall blocks known and emerging attacks using firewall rules. When you first install the WAF, it will be in learning mode. This allows Wordfence to learn about your site so that we can understand how to protect it and how to allow normal visitors through the firewall. We recommend you let Wordfence learn for a week before you enable the firewall.'=>'Wordfence Web应用进程防火墙使用防火墙规则阻止已知和新兴的攻击。 首次安装WAF时，它将处于学习模式。 这允许Wordfence了解您的网站，以便我们了解如何保护它以及如何允许普通访问者通过防火墙。 我们建议您在启用防火墙之前让Wordfence学习一周。','Web Application Firewall (WAF)'=>'Web应用进程防火墙(WAF)','This is where you can monitor the work Wordfence is doing to protect your site and also where you can manage the options to optimize the firewall\'s configuration.'=>'您可以在此处监控Wordfence为保护您的站点所做的工作，以及您可以在哪里管理优化防火墙配置的选项。','The Wordfence firewall protects your sites from attackers'=>'Wordfence防火墙可以保护您的站点免受攻击者的攻击','Manage global and advanced firewall options'=>'管理全局和高级防火墙选项','All Firewall Options'=>'所有防火墙选项','Block traffic by country, IP, IP range, user agent, referrer, or hostname'=>'按国家/地区，IP，IP范围，用户代理，引荐来源或主机名阻止流量','Block crawlers that are using too many resources or stealing content'=>'屏蔽使用过多资源或采集内容的爬网进程','Rate Limiting'=>'限速','Brute Force Protection Status'=>'强力保护状态','Manage Brute Force Protection'=>'管理强力保护','Stops Password Guessing Attacks'=>'阻止密码猜测攻击',': Disabled'=>':禁用','Brute Force Protection'=>'强力保护','Enable'=>'启用','Blocks requests from known malicious IPs'=>'屏蔽已知恶意IP的请求','Disabled'=>'停用','Enabled'=>'启动','Firewall Rules Status'=>'防火墙规则状态','Manage Firewall Rules'=>'管理防火墙规则','Rule updates delayed by 30 days'=>'规则更新延迟30天','Rules updated in real-time'=>'规则实时更新','Community'=>'社区','Firewall Rules: '=>'防火墙规则： ','https://www.wordfence.com/help/firewall/#firewall-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/firewall/#firewall-status','Web Application Firewall Status'=>'Web应用防火墙状态','Manage WAF'=>'管理WAF','Stops Complex Attacks'=>'阻止复杂的攻击','Currently in Learning Mode'=>'目前处于学习模式','Blocking Options'=>'锁定选项','All blocking rules you create will show here. You can manage them as well as remove or modify them from the same location.'=>'您创建的所有屏蔽规则都将在此处显示。 您可以管理它们，也可以从同一位置删除或修改它们。','All of the blocking rules you create are now in one central location. Simply choose the block type and enter the details for the rule you want to create. Premium users have access to advanced country blocking options, found via the <strong>Options</strong> link.'=>'您创建的所有屏蔽规则现在都位于一个中心位置。 只需选择块类型，然后输入要创建的规则的详细信息。 高级用户可以访问通过<strong>选项</strong>链接找到的高级国家/地区屏蔽选项。','Here\'s where you\'ll see all the blocking rules you\'ve created. You can also manage them as well as remove or modify them from this table.'=>'在这里，您将看到您创建的所有屏蔽规则。 您还可以管理它们以及从此表中删除或修改它们。','Manage Blocking Rules'=>'管理屏蔽规则','All of your blocking rules are in one central location. Choose the Block Type, then enter the details for the rule. Once it has been added, you\'ll see it saved as a rule for your site.'=>'您的所有屏蔽规则都位于一个中心位置。 选择“阻止类型”，然后输入规则的详细信息。 添加完成后，您会看到它已保存为您网站的规则。','Blocking Builder'=>'屏蔽生成器','Wordfence lets you take control of protecting your site with powerful blocking features. Block traffic based on IP, IP range, hostname, browser, or referrer. Country blocking is available for Premium customers.'=>'Wordfence可让您通过强大的阻止功能控制保护您的网站。 根据IP，IP范围，主机名，浏览器或引荐来阻止流量。 高级客户可以使用国家/地区封锁。','Edit Blocking Rule'=>'编辑屏蔽规则','Create a Blocking Rule'=>'创建屏蔽规则','More Information'=>'更多的信息','<strong>Note:</strong> The GeoIP database that is required for country blocking has been updated to a new format. This new format requires sites to run PHP 5.4 or newer, and this site is on PHP %s. To ensure country blocking continues functioning, please update PHP.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>国家/地区阻止所需的GeoIP数据库已更新为新格式。 这种新格式要求站点运行PHP 5.4或更高版本，但此站点的PHP版本为%s。要确保国家/地区阻止继续正常运行，请更新PHP。','Turn On'=>'开启','<strong>Note:</strong> Blocking is disabled when the option "Enable Rate Limiting and Advanced Blocking" is off.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>当“启用速率限制和高级阻止”选项关闭时，禁用阻止。','Blocking'=>'拦截','Web Application Firewall'=>'Web应用防火墙','Importing and exporting of options has moved to the Tools page'=>'导入和导出选项已移至“工具”页面','Import/Export Options'=>'导入/导出选项','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Global Options</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wf-hidden-xs">关于全局选项</span>','Are you sure you want to restore the default global settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page. Your configured license key and alert emails will not be changed.'=>'您确定要恢复默认的全局设置吗？ 这将撤消您对此页面上的选项所做的任何自定义更改。 您配置的许可证密钥和警报电子邮件不会更改。','Back<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> to Dashboard</span>'=>'返回<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> 到仪表板</span>','Wordfence Global Options'=>'Wordfence全局选项','No Thanks'=>'不用了，谢谢','Yes Please'=>'是的，请','Rate limiting based on type of request (human vs crawler) may be less accurate because this prevents loading the extra JavaScript used for that identification.'=>'基于请求类型（人类与爬虫）的速率限制可能不太准确，因为这可以防止加载用于该标识的额外JavaScript。','Greetings! The default configuration for Wordfence Live Traffic has changed. The new default saves only logins and blocked requests, while this site is currently recording all traffic. Would you like to change to the new default?'=>'您好！ Wordfence 实时流量的默认配置已更改。 新的默认设置仅保存登录和被阻止的请求，而此站点当前正在记录所有流量。 您想更改为新的默认值吗？','Recommended Settings Change'=>'推荐设置更改','The main navigation no longer includes an <strong>Options</strong> link. Options are now accessed via the <strong>Options</strong> link on each feature\'s main page. Live Traffic is now located in the Tools section, and blocking is found under the Firewall. Shortcuts to add a <strong>Blocking</strong> link back to the main navigation are available under Blocking options.'=>'主导航不再包含<strong>选项</strong>链接。 现在可以通过每个功能主页上的<strong>选项</strong>链接访问选项。 实时流量现在位于“工具”部分，并且可以在防火墙下找到阻止。 阻止选项下提供了将<strong>阻止</strong>链接添加回主导航的快捷方式。','Updated Navigation'=>'更新导航','Manage your Wordfence license, see alerts and automatic plugin updates, and import/export your settings.'=>'管理您的Wordfence许可证，查看警报和自动插件更新，以及导入/导出您的设置。','Each feature contains a status percentage reminding you at a high level of what\'s enabled, disabled, or needing your attention. The Notifications section highlights actions you need to take.'=>'每个功能都包含一个状态百分比，提醒您高级别启用，禁用或需要您注意的内容。 通知部分突出显示您需要采取的操作。','Monitor Your Wordfence Protection'=>'监控您的Wordfence保护','This update includes a number of significant interface changes. We\'d like to walk you through  some of them, but you can bypass the tour for a section at any time by closing the dialogs.'=>'此更新包括许多重要的界面更改。 我们想引导您完成其中的一些内容，但是您可以通过关闭对话框随时绕过巡视。','You have successfully updated to Wordfence %s'=>'您已成功更新为Wordfence %s','Got it'=>'知道了','You\'ll find this icon throughout the plugin. Clicking it will show you the options and features for each section of Wordfence. From the dashboard, you can find the <strong>Global Options</strong> for Wordfence such as alerts, automatic updates, and managing your site\'s Premium License.'=>'您会在整个插件中找到这个图标。 单击它将显示Wordfence的每个部分的选项和功能。 在仪表板中，您可以找到Wordfence的<strong>全局选项</strong>，例如警报，自动更新和管理站点的高级许可证。','Global Wordfence Options'=>'全局Wordfence选项','Previous'=>'上一页','Each feature contains a status that reminds you what\'s enabled, disabled or needs attention. The Notifications section will highlight actions you need to take.'=>'每个功能都包含一个状态，提醒您启用，禁用或需要注意的内容。 通知部分将突出显示您需要采取的操作。','Easily Monitor Your Wordfence Protection'=>'轻松监控您的Wordfence保护','Next'=>'下一页','The Wordfence Dashboard provides valuable insights into the current state of your site\'s security. You\'ll find useful data summarized here as well as important status updates and notifications.'=>'Wordfence仪表板提供有关站点安全性当前状态的宝贵见解。 您将在此处找到有用的数据以及重要的状态更新和通知。','This is your Dashboard'=>'这是您的控制面板','Manage global options for Wordfence such as alerts, premium status, and more'=>'管理Wordfence的全局选项，例如警报，高级状态等','Global Options'=>'全局选项','Find the documentation and help you need'=>'查找文件并提供所需帮助','Help'=>'帮助','Live Traffic, Whois Lookup, Import/Export, and Diagnostics'=>'实时流量、Whois查询、导入/导出和诊断','Tools'=>'工具','Review Payment Method'=>'查看付款方式','in 1 day'=>'在1天内','Update Payment Method'=>'更新付款方式','License renews %s'=>'许可证续订%s','in %d days'=>'在%d 天内','tomorrow'=>'明天','today'=>'今天','Payment Method Invalid'=>'付款方式无效','Payment Method Missing'=>'付款方式缺少','Payment Method Expired'=>'付款方式已过期','Payment Method Expiring'=>'付款方式到期','Auto-renew is disabled'=>'自动续订已禁用','Premium License Expiring'=>'高级许可证到期','Upgrade to Premium'=>'升级到高级版','Renew License'=>'更新授权','License is expired'=>'许可证已过期','Premium Protection Disabled'=>'高级保护已禁用','Reset License'=>'重置许可证','License already in use'=>'许可证已在使用中','Premium License Conflict'=>'高级许可冲突','Scan Status'=>'扫描状态','Manage Scan'=>'管理扫描','Detection of security issues'=>'检测安全问题','Scan'=>'扫描','https://www.wordfence.com/help/dashboard/#dashboard-status'=>'https://www.wordfence.com/help/dashboard/#dashboard-status','Firewall Status'=>'防火墙状态','Manage Firewall'=>'管理防火墙','Protection from known and emerging threats'=>'防范已知和新出现的威胁','WAF Currently in Learning Mode'=>'WAF目前处于学习模式','Firewall'=